{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2017/10/16/music_recommend_1-5/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"e3e1ca23-9a89-5bc7-bcaf-31f173d51d62","html":"<p>上半年在空间和Maliut公众号同步更新的音乐推荐歌单，目前处于停更状态<em>(:зゝ∠)</em></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://music.163.com/#/m/playlist?id=602753137&#x26;userid=248409876\">歌单网易云链接</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"vol1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vol1\" aria-label=\"vol1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Vol.1</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/04d6f809344ec24cb93fcbd7e0f191bb/9657e/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/04d6f809344ec24cb93fcbd7e0f191bb/066f9/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/04d6f809344ec24cb93fcbd7e0f191bb/b9e9c/1.jpg 100w,\n/static/04d6f809344ec24cb93fcbd7e0f191bb/e07e9/1.jpg 200w,\n/static/04d6f809344ec24cb93fcbd7e0f191bb/066f9/1.jpg 400w,\n/static/04d6f809344ec24cb93fcbd7e0f191bb/b4294/1.jpg 600w,\n/static/04d6f809344ec24cb93fcbd7e0f191bb/4b190/1.jpg 800w,\n/static/04d6f809344ec24cb93fcbd7e0f191bb/9657e/1.jpg 1216w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>这期以轻音乐为主，个人听轻音乐的历史也蛮长了，所以推荐也从这类音乐开始。一些极为著名的曲子就不列了（风居住的街道，日晷之梦，river flows in you,etc.）</p>\n<h3 id=\"1kan-r-gao-for-river-pianosarah--tommys-version\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1kan-r-gao-for-river-pianosarah--tommys-version\" aria-label=\"1kan r gao for river pianosarah  tommys version permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.Kan R. Gao-For River-Piano(Sarah &#x26; Tommy's Version)</h3>\n<p>来自To the moon的游戏配乐，极具剧情表现力的原创音乐是这部RPGMAKER游戏的两大台柱之一，这个版本的main theme变奏知名度比Johnny版本的小，我个人偏爱这个版本多一些。</p>\n<h3 id=\"2kan-r-gao-moonwisher\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2kan-r-gao-moonwisher\" aria-label=\"2kan r gao moonwisher permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.Kan R. Gao-Moonwisher</h3>\n<p>第二首依旧出自To the moon，John和River第一次见面的主题音乐，抒情满分的曲子。</p>\n<h3 id=\"3laura-shigihara-everythings-alright\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3laura-shigihara-everythings-alright\" aria-label=\"3laura shigihara everythings alright permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3.Laura Shigihara-Everything‘s Alright</h3>\n<p>To the Moon三连击（笑），这首插曲是整个游戏中唯一有词的歌，在游戏后期出现的时候催泪效果拔群。</p>\n<!-- more -->\n<h3 id=\"4麻枝准-夏影\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4%E9%BA%BB%E6%9E%9D%E5%87%86-%E5%A4%8F%E5%BD%B1\" aria-label=\"4麻枝准 夏影 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4.麻枝准-夏影</h3>\n<p>Air游戏配乐，一听就是夏天气氛的音乐。事实上高中第一次听的时候我没有玩过air，但依旧立刻喜欢上了这首曲子，如今重听这首曲子总会让我想起高中的夏日时光。</p>\n<h3 id=\"5麻枝准-渚\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5%E9%BA%BB%E6%9E%9D%E5%87%86-%E6%B8%9A\" aria-label=\"5麻枝准 渚 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5.麻枝准-渚</h3>\n<p>出自Clannad，古河渚的角色曲，整部游戏中印象最深的曲子，节奏把握也恰到好处。</p>\n<h3 id=\"6martin-ermen-apologize\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6martin-ermen-apologize\" aria-label=\"6martin ermen apologize permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6.Martin Ermen-Apologize</h3>\n<p>纯音乐版本更加注重抒情，钢琴代替人声带来了不同的表现力。</p>\n<h3 id=\"7骆集益-1945\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#7%E9%AA%86%E9%9B%86%E7%9B%8A-1945\" aria-label=\"7骆集益 1945 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>7.骆集益-1945</h3>\n<p>出自电影海角七号，最早听到这首曲子是因为高中的下课铃声。0:20开始的几个小节尤为让人印象深刻。</p>\n<h3 id=\"8全秀妍-안녕-나의-은빛-돌고래-piano-solo\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#8%E5%85%A8%E7%A7%80%E5%A6%8D-%EC%95%88%EB%85%95-%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98-%EC%9D%80%EB%B9%9B-%EB%8F%8C%EA%B3%A0%EB%9E%98-piano-solo\" aria-label=\"8全秀妍 안녕 나의 은빛 돌고래 piano solo permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>8.全秀妍-안녕, 나의 은빛 돌고래 (Piano Solo)</h3>\n<p>你好，我的银色海豚。温柔的钢琴曲，适合情绪安稳时听，亦可助眠。</p>\n<h3 id=\"9薛啸秋-卡农的幻想\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#9%E8%96%9B%E5%95%B8%E7%A7%8B-%E5%8D%A1%E5%86%9C%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%BB%E6%83%B3\" aria-label=\"9薛啸秋 卡农的幻想 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>9.薛啸秋-卡农的幻想</h3>\n<p>钢琴和提琴完美合作的代表，卡农就不需要我多介绍了，这个版本也是我最喜欢的卡农之一。</p>\n<h1 id=\"vol2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vol2\" aria-label=\"vol2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Vol.2</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/af542187d8c5c413f7279f1735a9b7a6/4b190/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/af542187d8c5c413f7279f1735a9b7a6/066f9/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/af542187d8c5c413f7279f1735a9b7a6/b9e9c/2.jpg 100w,\n/static/af542187d8c5c413f7279f1735a9b7a6/e07e9/2.jpg 200w,\n/static/af542187d8c5c413f7279f1735a9b7a6/066f9/2.jpg 400w,\n/static/af542187d8c5c413f7279f1735a9b7a6/b4294/2.jpg 600w,\n/static/af542187d8c5c413f7279f1735a9b7a6/4b190/2.jpg 800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>本期依旧以轻音乐专题，以游戏和动画配乐为主。</p>\n<h3 id=\"10szak-ナグルファルの船上にて--orgel-ver-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#10szak-%E3%83%8A%E3%82%B0%E3%83%AB%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%83%AB%E3%81%AE%E8%88%B9%E4%B8%8A%E3%81%AB%E3%81%A6--orgel-ver-\" aria-label=\"10szak ナグルファルの船上にて  orgel ver  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>10.Szak-ナグルファルの船上にて -Orgel Ver.-</h3>\n<p>出自素晴日的游戏配乐。作为与某寒蝉类似的中段猎奇结局治愈的作品，这种矛盾在这首曲子上也得以表现。ナグルファル（纳吉尔法），是北欧神话中的大船，整个船据说是用死者的指甲所建成。当这艘船完成的时候，就是北欧诸神和巨人族的最后大战之时“诸神的黄昏”。在诸神的黄昏，纳吉尔法上载满巨人和来自冥界的死者进攻诸神们的宫殿。而带着这么一个悲壮标题的曲子是八音盒主役的抒情曲。标题和游戏剧情暗合，音乐本身的气氛舒缓优美，这也是这部游戏的亮点之一。</p>\n<h3 id=\"11szak-夜の向日葵\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#11szak-%E5%A4%9C%E3%81%AE%E5%90%91%E6%97%A5%E8%91%B5\" aria-label=\"11szak 夜の向日葵 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>11.Szak-夜の向日葵</h3>\n<p>同样出自素晴日，水上由岐的主题音乐。整首曲子极具空灵感，让人想起夜晚晴朗的天空，还有天空下仰望的少女。</p>\n<h3 id=\"12szak-小さな旋律\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#12szak-%E5%B0%8F%E3%81%95%E3%81%AA%E6%97%8B%E5%BE%8B\" aria-label=\"12szak 小さな旋律 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>12.Szak-小さな旋律</h3>\n<p>素晴日三连击（笑x2），这首曲子在我心目中是整个游戏的灵魂。在一切混乱过去后来之不易的美好的每一天，和这首曲子一样带着沉重和感激。我不知道这是不是作者想要传达给玩家的，但它着实给我留下了深刻印象。</p>\n<h3 id=\"13朝倉紀行-departurepiano-solo\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#13%E6%9C%9D%E5%80%89%E7%B4%80%E8%A1%8C-departurepiano-solo\" aria-label=\"13朝倉紀行 departurepiano solo permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>13.朝倉紀行-Departure(Piano Solo)</h3>\n<p>出自浪客剑心配乐。一部老动画，但音乐令人惊异的超前。一首钢琴独奏完美映出了悲伤和决绝的心。</p>\n<h3 id=\"14key-sounds-label-bloom-of-youth\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#14key-sounds-label-bloom-of-youth\" aria-label=\"14key sounds label bloom of youth permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>14.Key Sounds Label-Bloom of Youth</h3>\n<p>出自库特Wafter的游戏配乐，依旧是大魔王熟悉的抒情风格。标题可以直译成绽放的青春，年轻真好啊（老头脸）</p>\n<h3 id=\"15天門-シュンとの时间\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#15%E5%A4%A9%E9%96%80-%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A5%E3%83%B3%E3%81%A8%E3%81%AE%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4\" aria-label=\"15天門 シュンとの时间 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>15.天門-シュンとの时间</h3>\n<p>出自新海诚的动画电影 追逐繁星的孩子。这也是最后一部新海诚和天門合作的电影。新海诚在此之前的大部分作品包括秒五音乐均由天門执笔，其唯美而带有一丝忧伤的曲风和新海诚的剧情相得益彰，这首曲子很好地展现了这一点。</p>\n<h3 id=\"16angel-note-aliare-on-piano\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#16angel-note-aliare-on-piano\" aria-label=\"16angel note aliare on piano permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>16.Angel Note-Aliare ~on piano~</h3>\n<p>出自游戏 春季限定 的配乐，忧伤气质的钢琴曲，中段主题旋律相当抓人耳朵。</p>\n<h3 id=\"17梶浦由记-m01\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#17%E6%A2%B6%E6%B5%A6%E7%94%B1%E8%AE%B0-m01\" aria-label=\"17梶浦由记 m01 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>17.梶浦由记-M01</h3>\n<p>出自空之境界 Vol.2 杀人考察（前）。温柔的钢琴旋律贯穿始终，比同专辑的M18显得更婉转一些。（又及空境各个专辑曲目名有毒，有兴趣可以看看）</p>\n<h3 id=\"18松田彬人-pure-heart\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#18%E6%9D%BE%E7%94%B0%E5%BD%AC%E4%BA%BA-pure-heart\" aria-label=\"18松田彬人 pure heart permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>18.松田彬人-pure heart</h3>\n<p>出自动画 初恋限定。小心翼翼的钢琴独奏，气氛塑造极佳的曲子，适合看原作漫画的BGM（雾）</p>\n<h1 id=\"vol3\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vol3\" aria-label=\"vol3 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Vol.3</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1eb0d56b3558df86ca7f600cef888d0c/29d31/3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"3\"\n        src=\"/static/1eb0d56b3558df86ca7f600cef888d0c/066f9/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1eb0d56b3558df86ca7f600cef888d0c/b9e9c/3.jpg 100w,\n/static/1eb0d56b3558df86ca7f600cef888d0c/e07e9/3.jpg 200w,\n/static/1eb0d56b3558df86ca7f600cef888d0c/066f9/3.jpg 400w,\n/static/1eb0d56b3558df86ca7f600cef888d0c/b4294/3.jpg 600w,\n/static/1eb0d56b3558df86ca7f600cef888d0c/29d31/3.jpg 700w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>本期是韩国抒情钢琴曲专题，适合充实读书/作业用歌单。以小众作者为主，知名钢琴家如李闰珉、全素妍等的作品就不推荐了。</p>\n<h3 id=\"19love-rabbit-마음이-계절에-흔들리다（心情随着季节波动）\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#19love-rabbit-%EB%A7%88%EC%9D%8C%EC%9D%B4-%EA%B3%84%EC%A0%88%EC%97%90-%ED%9D%94%EB%93%A4%EB%A6%AC%EB%8B%A4%EF%BC%88%E5%BF%83%E6%83%85%E9%9A%8F%E7%9D%80%E5%AD%A3%E8%8A%82%E6%B3%A2%E5%8A%A8%EF%BC%89\" aria-label=\"19love rabbit 마음이 계절에 흔들리다（心情随着季节波动） permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>19.Love Rabbit-마음이 계절에 흔들리다（心情随着季节波动）</h3>\n<h3 id=\"20love-rabbit-사랑이-꽃피는-나무（爱之树）\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#20love-rabbit-%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%EC%9D%B4-%EA%BD%83%ED%94%BC%EB%8A%94-%EB%82%98%EB%AC%B4%EF%BC%88%E7%88%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%A0%91%EF%BC%89\" aria-label=\"20love rabbit 사랑이 꽃피는 나무（爱之树） permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>20.Love Rabbit-사랑이 꽃피는 나무（爱之树）</h3>\n<h3 id=\"21love-rabbit-추억은-사랑을-닮았다（回忆中的爱情）\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#21love-rabbit-%EC%B6%94%EC%96%B5%EC%9D%80-%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%EC%9D%84-%EB%8B%AE%EC%95%98%EB%8B%A4%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%9E%E5%BF%86%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E7%88%B1%E6%83%85%EF%BC%89\" aria-label=\"21love rabbit 추억은 사랑을 닮았다（回忆中的爱情） permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>21.Love Rabbit-추억은 사랑을 닮았다（回忆中的爱情）</h3>\n<h3 id=\"22love-rabbit-이-음악이-들리니（听到这音乐了吗？）\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#22love-rabbit-%EC%9D%B4-%EC%9D%8C%EC%95%85%EC%9D%B4-%EB%93%A4%EB%A6%AC%EB%8B%88%EF%BC%88%E5%90%AC%E5%88%B0%E8%BF%99%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E4%BA%86%E5%90%97%EF%BC%9F%EF%BC%89\" aria-label=\"22love rabbit 이 음악이 들리니（听到这音乐了吗？） permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>22.Love Rabbit-이 음악이 들리니?（听到这音乐了吗？）</h3>\n<p>首先是Love Rabbit的四首曲子，曲风温柔，心情平和时食用更佳。与各类描写细腻的日系言情作品相性良好，比如《我想吃掉你的胰脏》（咦？）</p>\n<h3 id=\"23reve-화華\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#23reve-%ED%99%94%E8%8F%AF\" aria-label=\"23reve 화華 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>23.Reve-화(華)</h3>\n<p>百度找不到的作者=。=Reve重名的太多了。曲子的情绪起伏比较大，旋律也可以用漂亮来形容。</p>\n<h3 id=\"24july-달빛이-저무는-밤（月光迟暮之夜）\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#24july-%EB%8B%AC%EB%B9%9B%EC%9D%B4-%EC%A0%80%EB%AC%B4%EB%8A%94-%EB%B0%A4%EF%BC%88%E6%9C%88%E5%85%89%E8%BF%9F%E6%9A%AE%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%9C%EF%BC%89\" aria-label=\"24july 달빛이 저무는 밤（月光迟暮之夜） permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>24.July-달빛이 저무는 밤（月光迟暮之夜）</h3>\n<p>July海量节奏曲中的清流。钢琴solo引导全曲，中段提琴伴奏的插入也十分惊艳。</p>\n<h3 id=\"25조한빛-난-아직-겨울（我还在冬天）\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#25%EC%A1%B0%ED%95%9C%EB%B9%9B-%EB%82%9C-%EC%95%84%EC%A7%81-%EA%B2%A8%EC%9A%B8%EF%BC%88%E6%88%91%E8%BF%98%E5%9C%A8%E5%86%AC%E5%A4%A9%EF%BC%89\" aria-label=\"25조한빛 난 아직 겨울（我还在冬天） permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>25.조한빛-난 아직 겨울（我还在冬天）</h3>\n<p>这个作者的曲子很少但是作品质量都很高，有兴趣可以查询조한빛（这位重名不多）的其他作品，这里不多列。</p>\n<h3 id=\"26crepe-4월의-눈동자를-지닌-소녀（the-girl-with-april-in-her-eyes）\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#26crepe-4%EC%9B%94%EC%9D%98-%EB%88%88%EB%8F%99%EC%9E%90%EB%A5%BC-%EC%A7%80%EB%8B%8C-%EC%86%8C%EB%85%80%EF%BC%88the-girl-with-april-in-her-eyes%EF%BC%89\" aria-label=\"26crepe 4월의 눈동자를 지닌 소녀（the girl with april in her eyes） permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>26.Crepe-4월의 눈동자를 지닌 소녀（The Girl With April In Her Eyes）</h3>\n<h3 id=\"27crepe-같은-하늘-아래에-서다（under-the-same-sky）\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#27crepe-%EA%B0%99%EC%9D%80-%ED%95%98%EB%8A%98-%EC%95%84%EB%9E%98%EC%97%90-%EC%84%9C%EB%8B%A4%EF%BC%88under-the-same-sky%EF%BC%89\" aria-label=\"27crepe 같은 하늘 아래에 서다（under the same sky） permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>27.Crepe-같은 하늘 아래에 서다（Under The Same Sky）</h3>\n<p>同一个作者，一首致郁，一首治愈。作者对音乐表达的情绪把控相当好（又及：这位作者的专辑封面画风着实独具特色）</p>\n<h1 id=\"vol4\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vol4\" aria-label=\"vol4 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Vol.4</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f8c85706bdaa6bbe823421f83546221b/4b190/4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"4\"\n        src=\"/static/f8c85706bdaa6bbe823421f83546221b/066f9/4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f8c85706bdaa6bbe823421f83546221b/b9e9c/4.jpg 100w,\n/static/f8c85706bdaa6bbe823421f83546221b/e07e9/4.jpg 200w,\n/static/f8c85706bdaa6bbe823421f83546221b/066f9/4.jpg 400w,\n/static/f8c85706bdaa6bbe823421f83546221b/b4294/4.jpg 600w,\n/static/f8c85706bdaa6bbe823421f83546221b/4b190/4.jpg 800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>东方专题，选曲多为本作系列BGM改，兼有纯音乐和人声歌曲。</p>\n<h3 id=\"28foxtail-grass-studio-瞳の中で踊り踊られ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#28foxtail-grass-studio-%E7%9E%B3%E3%81%AE%E4%B8%AD%E3%81%A7%E8%B8%8A%E3%82%8A%E8%B8%8A%E3%82%89%E3%82%8C\" aria-label=\"28foxtail grass studio 瞳の中で踊り踊られ permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>28.Foxtail-Grass Studio-瞳の中で踊り踊られ</h3>\n<p>原曲少女さとり～3rd eye，古明地觉的角色曲。个人最喜欢的一个改曲版本，提琴和哥特曲风的搭配相得益彰，游戏内的渲染也做得很足。</p>\n<h3 id=\"29nayuta-绯色月下、狂咲ノ絶\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#29nayuta-%E7%BB%AF%E8%89%B2%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%8B%E3%80%81%E7%8B%82%E5%92%B2%E3%83%8E%E7%B5%B6\" aria-label=\"29nayuta 绯色月下、狂咲ノ絶 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>29.nayuta-绯色月下、狂咲ノ絶</h3>\n<h3 id=\"30nayuta-滲色血界、月狂ノ獄\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#30nayuta-%E6%BB%B2%E8%89%B2%E8%A1%80%E7%95%8C%E3%80%81%E6%9C%88%E7%8B%82%E3%83%8E%E7%8D%84\" aria-label=\"30nayuta 滲色血界、月狂ノ獄 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>30.nayuta-滲色血界、月狂ノ獄</h3>\n<p>大小姐二小姐病娇曲两连发，本人不对听完后的各类不适反应和兴奋（？）反应负责（又及这种中二爆表的标题不止这两首，有兴趣的可以参见评论区）。</p>\n<h3 id=\"31morrigan-第九楽章-dawn-of-east-end\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#31morrigan-%E7%AC%AC%E4%B9%9D%E6%A5%BD%E7%AB%A0-dawn-of-east-end\" aria-label=\"31morrigan 第九楽章 dawn of east end permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>31.Morrigan-第九楽章 Dawn of East End</h3>\n<p>原曲童祭。比原曲节奏慢一些的交响乐，气势豁然开阔，个人比较喜欢的版本（开头谜之像舌尖上的中国）。</p>\n<h3 id=\"32foxtail-grass-studio-雨待ち傘\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#32foxtail-grass-studio-%E9%9B%A8%E5%BE%85%E3%81%A1%E5%82%98\" aria-label=\"32foxtail grass studio 雨待ち傘 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>32.Foxtail-Grass Studio-雨待ち傘</h3>\n<p>原曲緑眼のジェラシー，地灵殿 水桥帕露西的主题曲「绿眼的嫉妒」。和第一首是一个社团的作品，原曲的旋律就很漂亮，改曲甚至做得更完美，气氛营造极佳（该社团的其他东方同人作品同样不错，例如云流れ）。</p>\n<h3 id=\"33ししまいブラザーズ-诗をひとつまみ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#33%E3%81%97%E3%81%97%E3%81%BE%E3%81%84%E3%83%96%E3%83%A9%E3%82%B6%E3%83%BC%E3%82%BA-%E8%AF%97%E3%82%92%E3%81%B2%E3%81%A8%E3%81%A4%E3%81%BE%E3%81%BF\" aria-label=\"33ししまいブラザーズ 诗をひとつまみ permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>33.ししまいブラザーズ-诗をひとつまみ</h3>\n<p>原曲冷吟闲酔，出自东方绯想天。zun和黄昏边境合作的格斗游戏（没毛病），这首的曲风活泼灵动，又有一丝神秘色彩。</p>\n<h3 id=\"34golden-city-factory-东の国の眠らない夜\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#34golden-city-factory-%E4%B8%9C%E3%81%AE%E5%9B%BD%E3%81%AE%E7%9C%A0%E3%82%89%E3%81%AA%E3%81%84%E5%A4%9C\" aria-label=\"34golden city factory 东の国の眠らない夜 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>34.Golden City Factory-东の国の眠らない夜</h3>\n<h3 id=\"35黒ヶ音研究室-refined-vision\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#35%E9%BB%92%E3%83%B6%E9%9F%B3%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%AE%A4-refined-vision\" aria-label=\"35黒ヶ音研究室 refined vision permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>35.黒ヶ音研究室-Refined Vision</h3>\n<h3 id=\"36彩音-xi-on-ネイティブフェイス\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#36%E5%BD%A9%E9%9F%B3-xi-on-%E3%83%8D%E3%82%A4%E3%83%86%E3%82%A3%E3%83%96%E3%83%95%E3%82%A7%E3%82%A4%E3%82%B9\" aria-label=\"36彩音 xi on ネイティブフェイス permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>36.彩音 ~xi-on~-ネイティブフェイス</h3>\n<p>最后是三首来自不同社团的节奏类作品，东方作为持续十余年的火爆IP，好的同人乐曲数不胜数，这里我只是摘取了极小的一部分做了推荐，权当抛砖引玉。欢迎各位潜藏的大佬也来推荐曲子=。=</p>\n<h1 id=\"vol5\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vol5\" aria-label=\"vol5 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Vol.5</h1>\n<p>![](<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ee42e22dc2c300a89c5c06c76a72f9c6/4b190/5.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"/static/ee42e22dc2c300a89c5c06c76a72f9c6/066f9/5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ee42e22dc2c300a89c5c06c76a72f9c6/b9e9c/5.jpg 100w,\n/static/ee42e22dc2c300a89c5c06c76a72f9c6/e07e9/5.jpg 200w,\n/static/ee42e22dc2c300a89c5c06c76a72f9c6/066f9/5.jpg 400w,\n/static/ee42e22dc2c300a89c5c06c76a72f9c6/b4294/5.jpg 600w,\n/static/ee42e22dc2c300a89c5c06c76a72f9c6/4b190/5.jpg 800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>本期是白噪音专题，白噪声或白噪音，是一种功率频谱密度为常数的随机信号或随机过程。换句话说，此信号在各个频段上的功率是一样的，由于白光是由各种频率（颜色）的单色光混合而成，因而此信号的这种具有平坦功率谱的性质被称作是“白色的”，此信号也因此被称作白噪声。不同于其他噪音，白噪声会使人感到平静，更易集中注意力。同时白噪声相对舒缓、有规律，也可以帮助入睡。白噪声的代表有雨声、落叶声、海浪声、还有无聊老师上课的声音（雾）。同时白噪音兼有通常耳机播放音乐的覆盖效果，可以有效抵抗不很强的嘈杂声，例如在图书馆、宿舍旁人的键盘鼠标声，在教室自习走廊下课杂音等等（均亲测）。</p>\n<h3 id=\"3710-hz-alpha-thunderstorm-extended-version\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3710-hz-alpha-thunderstorm-extended-version\" aria-label=\"3710 hz alpha thunderstorm extended version permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>37.10 Hz Alpha Thunderstorm (Extended Version)</h3>\n<h3 id=\"38-rainy-mood\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#38-rainy-mood\" aria-label=\"38 rainy mood permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>38. Rainy Mood</h3>\n<p>虽然只有两首，但加起来90分钟，一首更比十首强（笑）。选择暴雨纯属个人口味。有一些网站也提供了白噪音自混成的功能，你可以自己选择白噪音的组合，例如<a href=\"http://asoftmurmur.com/\">http://asoftmurmur.com/</a>。</p>\n<p><del>下期更新时间照常未定，主题也未定 <em>(:зゝ∠)</em></del></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"日始之音 Vol.1~5","date":"2017-10-16","categories":"音乐","message":null,"tags":["音乐推荐"]},"fields":{"encrypted":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2017/01/20/qmnote/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"量子力学笔记"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2017/11/28/17autumn-event/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"捷号決戦！邀撃、レイテ沖海戦(前篇)"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"e3e1ca23-9a89-5bc7-bcaf-31f173d51d62","previousPostId":"73f1e3a5-958f-5f46-b1a0-a241a327c2a9","nextPostId":"53a84920-c3bb-59b6-a991-e3b4bfc18e1b"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1605745662","2212765230","2826202570","3000541721","3274528899","3390260504","3406122720","3823010829","689422991"]}